      "reference_id": "a7796bc3-9aad-4280-b3b8-94b629728f7a",
      "text": "Authors propse an automated system for detection of at—risk students called RADAR. The authors do a pilot test of the system on a set of students from a school district.",
      "provenance": {
        "page_id": "a7796bc3-9aad-4280-b3b8-94b629728f7a"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "an_4ffb14a2",
      "reference_id": "a7796bc3-9aad-4280-b3b8-94b629728f7a",
      "text": "The model uses data from multiple sources (multi-modal data sources), preprocesses it, performs feature selection and also returns predictions of performance/dropout. Authors argue that the approach on pilot tet achieved high accuracy. The system intends to provide continuous and automated monitoring of student progress. ",
